The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for error correction, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of probabilistic re-synthesis also suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves data processing and manipulation, which could fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
